Currently we have following major goals for 1.2 version of component: 

 * Add support for projection and folding
 * Support nesting of lists
 * Support styled regions. - Regions that are highlighted in the viewer and styled automatically. For example snippet of Java code
 * Implement importers/exporters for one or two popular Wiki markup languages.
 * Polish API, and improve widget extensibility.
 * Add support for basic tables.

We are planning to release 1.2 version of rich text viewer at the early start of 2009. 

